Achievements.Name: The Battlemaster
Achievements.Description: Do you have a taste for blood? Participate in battles and find out.

Achievements.Name: The Rules of Consecution
Achievements.Description: Are you keeping an eye on the chain count? Try to get as high a number as possible.

Achievements.Name: Death and Destruction
Achievements.Description: Do you want your party members to grow stronger? Try defeating lots of monsters.

Achievements.Name: Unleashing Secret Powers
Achievements.Description: Are you putting Timeshift to good use? Try using it as often as possible.

Achievements.Name: Timing is Everything
Achievements.Description: How is your hand-eye coordination? Try using Critical Triggers whenever possible.

Achievements.Name: The Guildmaster's Faith
Achievements.Description: Have you accepted the guild masters' challenges? Try finishing lots of guild tasks.

Achievements.Name: March of the Soldiers
Achievements.Description: Do you want a bigger party? Recruit some soldiers at a guild.

Achievements.Name: The Heir of Ultimate Fate
Achievements.Description: Have you been creating items? Try creating a certain one...

Achievements.Name: The Ravenous Hunter
Achievements.Description: How is Mr. Diggs? Try harvesting a certain item...

Achievements.Name: Guru of the Mystic
Achievements.Description: Do you like collecting items? Try obtaining a certain one...

Achievements.Name: Monster Dismantler
Achievements.Description: Are you collecting components? Try taking apart lots of monsters.

Achievements.Name: Reduce, Reuse, Recycle
Achievements.Description: Do you recycle? Try taking apart lots of equipment.

Achievements.Name: The Lone Fighter
Achievements.Description: Do you want a challenge? Defeat the monster that appears from a certain quest.

Achievements.Name: The Dragonslayer
Achievements.Description: For a bigger challenge, defeat the monster that appears from a certain quest.

Achievements.Name: The Great Soldier
Achievements.Description: For a huge challenge, defeat the monster that appears from a certain guild task.

Achievements.Name: Hero of the Dawn
Achievements.Description: For a great challenge, defeat the monster that appears from a certain guild task.

Achievements.Name: The Godslayer
Achievements.Description: For the biggest challenge of them all, defeat the monster they call The Fallen.

Achievements.Name: The Bloodhunter
Achievements.Description: You have defeated over 30 monsters in one battle. You must have lots of rare items!

Achievements.Name: Living Rich
Achievements.Description: You have obtained over 200,000G. Are you taking your friends out for nice meals?

Achievements.Name: Lost Words of the Gods
Achievements.Description: You have spent over 100,000G. Would you like some investment advice?

Achievements.Name: The Final Instance
Achievements.Description: You have finished the quest "Things Unchangeable." Congratulations!

Achievements.Name: The Last Remnant
Achievements.Description: You have defeated the Absolute Conqueror. Perhaps YOU are the Last Remnant...
